## Description {#details}

This file implements the APSInt class, which is a simple class that represents an arbitrary sized integer that knows its signedness.

<Link id="l00334" /><CodeLine lineNumber="334"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// We have a signedness mismatch. Check for negative values and do an</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00336" /><CodeLine lineNumber="336"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">if</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> (I1.isSigned()) &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
